      <title>英格兰银行希望关注私募股权杠杆率</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/bank-england-looks-shine-light-private-equity-leverage-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行一位官员周一表示，监管机构需要关注价值 8 万亿美元的全球私募股权行业，因为不透明的杠杆使得人们很难了解其对金融稳定、就业和增长构成的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/bank-england-looks-shine-light-private-equity-leverage-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:38:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管面临全球阻力，欧洲央行行长仍坚持多次降息计划</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-governors-stick-plan-multiple-rate-cuts-despite-global-headwinds-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行官员仍坚持今年多次降息的计划，尽管美国通胀上升推迟了美联储转向宽松政策的时间，而且中东紧张局势导致油价居高不下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-governors-stick-plan-multiple-rate-cuts-despite-global-headwinds-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 12:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员表示，欧洲公司、银行必须增加对关键矿产的投资</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/european-firms-banks-must-boost-investment-critical-minerals-official-says-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家欧盟资助组织的负责人表示，汽车制造商和金融机构等欧洲企业需要加大对该地区关键矿产的投资，以开发能源转型关键原材料的国内来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/european-firms-banks-must-boost-investment-critical-minerals-official-says-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 11:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收入较低的美国消费者面临贷款压力，而银行则缩减开支</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-consumers-lower-incomes-face-loan-stress-while-banks-pull-back-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据最近的数据和银行高管的数据，美国收入较低的借款人越来越难以偿还贷款，这促使银行在发放信用卡和汽车贷款时变得更加谨慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-consumers-lower-incomes-face-loan-stress-while-banks-pull-back-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:37:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
