    <item>
      <title>尽管通胀恐慌，美国债券多头仍倾向于最新抛售</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-bond-bulls-lean-into-latest-selloff-despite-inflation-scare-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[4月份迄今为止美国债券的大幅抛售促使一些投资者考虑向该资产类别配置更多资金，以在美联储降息之前锁定更高的收益率，尽管美国经济具有韧性，但这一前景仍然是投资者的基本预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-bond-bulls-lean-into-latest-selloff-despite-inflation-scare-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛表示，对冲基金借款触及五年来最高点</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-fund-borrowing-hits-five-year-peak-goldman-sachs-says-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛的一份报告显示，截至 4 月 19 日当周，全球对冲基金借款升至五年高位，对冲基金利用今年美国和欧洲股市首次大幅下跌的机会加大交易力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-fund-borrowing-hits-five-year-peak-goldman-sachs-says-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国梦的破灭迫使西方金融公司削减成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/souring-china-dreams-force-western-financial-firms-cut-costs-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在几年前，中国经济蓬勃发展带来的利润丰厚的商业前景导致西方金融公司（从投资银行到资产管理）竞相扩大业务范围并从世界各地招募人才。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/souring-china-dreams-force-western-financial-firms-cut-costs-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:42:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲斯托克指数小幅走高，银行盈利成为焦点；高尔普发光</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/europes-stoxx-climbs-with-bank-earnings-focus-galp-jumps-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周一小幅走高，投资者等待本周晚些时候几家大银行的盈利报告，而葡萄牙石油公司 Galp 在纳米比亚天然气勘探取得积极进展后，股价飙升至 16 年来的新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/europes-stoxx-climbs-with-bank-earnings-focus-galp-jumps-2024-04-22/</guid>
