    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长担心美联储式“点阵图”带来政治压力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-governors-fear-fed-style-dot-plot-would-invite-political-pressure-sources-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消息人士告诉路透，欧洲央行行长担心公布利率预测会招致各国政府施加压力，试图评估央行行长是否服务于其国内议程，这表明效仿美联储做法的想法可能很难接受。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/ecb-governors-fear-fed-style-dot-plot-would-invite-political-pressure-sources-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 06:03:06 GMT</pubDate>
